  "commentary": "**DEALER HEDGING COMMENTARY:**\n\nDealers are currently in a PIN regime with spot at 6551 sitting right between the massive +9.3B gamma wall at 6565 and -9B negative gamma pocket at 6500, creating a tight 65-point trading range where dealers will aggressively fade moves in either direction. The recent GEX surge combined with spot trading 26 points below the flip level at 6577 means dealers are actively buying this dip while simultaneously preparing to sell any rally back toward the 6580 max positive gamma level. Watch for strong support at 6565 (second largest positive wall) and potential acceleration if we break below 6500 where dealers flip to buying mode but price action becomes more volatile.",
